import AirbnbCerealBlack from "../../assets/fonts/AirbnbCerealBlack.ttf";

import AirbnbCerealBook from "../../assets/fonts/AirbnbCerealBook.ttf";
import AirbnbCerealLight from "../../assets/fonts/AirbnbCerealLight.ttf";

export const airbnbCerealLight = {
  fontFamily: "AirbnbCereal",
  fontStyle: "normal",
  fontDisplay: "swap",
  fontWeight: 300,
  src: `
    local('AirbnbCereal'),
    local('AirbnbCerealLight'),
    url(${AirbnbCerealLight}) format('woff2')
  `,
  unicodeRange:
    "U+0000-00FF, U+0131, U+0152-0153, U+02BB-02BC, U+02C6, U+02DA, U+02DC, U+2000-206F, U+2074, U+20AC, U+2122, U+2191, U+2193, U+2212, U+2215, U+FEFF",
};
